7. Minimal Translation Targets

Version 0.1 should stay disciplined and support a small number of high-value targets.

Recommended initial targets:

7.1 Structured Prose

For explanation, teaching, README generation, design notes.

7.2 JSON / YAML

For machine readability, config, serialization, schema portability.

7.3 Python Scaffold

For executable prototypes and agent architecture stubs.

7.4 Graph / Diagram Spec

For node-edge visualization, mermaid output, system maps.

7.5 Workflow Representation

For procedural execution:
Observe → Extract → Decide → Act → Record

These five targets are enough to prove the concept without overextending the system.

